# plan/facts/05-production-deployment-evidence.bn
#
# Evidence from production deployments + vendor engineering content.
# Per mizaj rule 11, vendor sources cap at L4 (0.40 ceiling). These
# don't lift umbrella confidences past their L3-mutawatir or L1 ceilings,
# but they STRENGTHEN the evidence chain and show that compound
# architectures are the production standard for hard reasoning.
#
# Specifically: Claude Code (Anthropic), Claude Opus 4.7 verifying its
# own outputs, NVIDIA NeMo Agent Toolkit, OpenAgentsControl on opencode.

